{
  "stem": "27409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then I was let out and had to work [INAUDIBLE] with the young people until the-- it was in a Saturday they made an agreement with the German [? pressed ?] to send us off.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had in the town an Einsatzgruppen, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Oldenburg. ?] They were the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Obersturm ?] [INAUDIBLE] the boss was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oldenburg. ?] And we had [? 10B ?] was the one who executed the people in this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were not pleasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They occupied the central hotel, where the execution were usually in the lift.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then, you had to take them out, or they threw them out in the front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember like the day and they're standing there, the SS guard with his medal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The [? beatings ?] where some officer, which [? shows ?] [? their ?] [INAUDIBLE] [? guard ?] this member was wearing uniform now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was a hard time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were not permitted to go out after 7 o'clock, if I remember well, for dark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was early morning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My aunt, the younger sister of my mother, came running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You are still home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Pack quickly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Ordered to go in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They instituted the ghetto, a few streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This is surrounded with barbed wires, and they made a gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "All had to be until 5 o'clock, 6 o'clock-- I don't remember, but in the evening to move in the ghetto-- the entire Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You had about 40,000 Jews in the town-- 30,000 Jews in the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But there were many Jews, which came from the surrounding-- which survived in the surrounding small townships and villages [? that ?] came all to the town.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
